  "description": "The Ubiquiti Swiss Army Knife Ultra is a compact indoor / outdoor PoE access point that delivers powerful wireless coverage and connectivity to your network. With its versatile mounting options and long-range antenna capabilities, the UK-Ultra is a true Swiss Army Knife of wireless connectivity. Experience exceptional wireless performance with Wi-Fi 5 (2x2 MIMO) technology, capable of supporting up to 200+ connected devices and enjoy smooth streaming, seamless file transfers, and lag-free online gaming.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Unmatched Versatility",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti Swiss Army Knife Ultra is a compact indoor / outdoor PoE access point that delivers powerful wireless coverage and connectivity to your network. With its versatile mounting options and long-range antenna capabilities, the UK-Ultra is a true Swiss Army Knife of wireless connectivity. Experience exceptional wireless performance with Wi-Fi 5 (2x2 MIMO) technology, capable of supporting up to 200+ connected devices and enjoy smooth streaming, seamless file transfers, and lag-free online gaming."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Effortless Deployment",
      "text": "The UK-Ultra is powered from an existing Ethernet network, eliminating the need for additional power cables. Its compact form factor allows for discreet mounting on wall, ceiling or pole, making it ideal for both indoor and outdoor deployments. You can expand the coverage with two RP-SMA connectors for optional external antennas (sold separately). The additional omnidirectional or directional antennas enable you to tailor the UK-Ultra's signal strength and direction to optimize coverage for your specific needs."
    }
  ],
